    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《MindsEye》战役</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《MindsEye》是一款剧情叙事驱动的惊悚风格单人动作冒险游戏，故事背景设定在近未来沙漠城市红石城。你将扮演雅各布·迪亚兹——一名退役士兵，因被植入了神秘的神经植入体而饱受支离破碎的记忆困扰。在电影化叙事的战役中，你将执行任务、揭开过往谜团，并直面一场涉及失控人工智能、腐败企业与无序军事力量的惊天阴谋——这场危机的波及范围远不止红石城本身。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/fe862671044a07cc6a6cb04b7357e9f6.poster.avif?t=1770203833\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/fe862671044a07cc6a6cb04b7357e9f6.webm?t=1770203833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>红石城</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >红石城是一座沙漠都市，尖端科技在这里随处可见。人工智能与机器人技术掌控着居民的日常生活，从商业贸易到治安安防无不深受影响。这座城市的表象之下，暗藏着无数秘密、重重危机与激烈冲突。从熠熠生辉的摩天楼群，到杂乱蔓延的工业区，再到地处偏僻的哨站据点，每个城区都是这个故事不可或缺的组成部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/8ad8e45d741bb836fe447d53a4fb610b.poster.avif?t=1770203833\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/8ad8e45d741bb836fe447d53a4fb610b.webm?t=1770203833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/8ad8e45d741bb836fe447d53a4fb610b.mp4?t=1770203833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战斗系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作的战斗系统互动丰富，讲究战术策略。利用敌人独特的行为模式智取对手，巧妙运用掩体与高低差优势，在第三人称视角下使用丰富武器库——包括手枪、冲锋枪、狙击步枪、能量武器与手榴弹等作战。你的无人机搭档DC2与你的神经植入体直接相连，可在战斗中执行黑客入侵、侦察探测与火力支援任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/8efd0d93b086298e165794f06aee6611.poster.avif?t=1770203833\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/8efd0d93b086298e165794f06aee6611.webm?t=1770203833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>驾驶和载具互动</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在执行任务时，你将亲自驾驭电动轿车、肌肉跑车、巡逻车及四轴无人机等多种载具。高速追逐、沙漠狂飙、工业区追击——这些激烈场景旨在考验你的驾驶技术，让动作体验高潮迭起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/cc8ca023b511def0f2f17d8e0e632884.poster.avif?t=1770203833\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/cc8ca023b511def0f2f17d8e0e632884.webm?t=1770203833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>源源不断的全新可玩内容</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事战役仅仅是个开端。《MindsEye》将定期推出源源不断的全新可玩内容。BARB团队开发并推出的全新任务、竞速、解谜与挑战内容，为你带来持续不断的新鲜惊喜。这个持续演进的世界，让玩家在主线剧情结束后仍能通过层出不穷的新玩法，持续体验《MindsEye》的魅力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/30e11e4e31b937575267497daec21c9c.poster.avif?t=1770203833\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/30e11e4e31b937575267497daec21c9c.webm?t=1770203833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>易上手的创作工具</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用我们简单易用的建造工具，你不只是在游玩，更是在创造。建造者模式提供3A级开发工具，包含资产库与光照系统，以及简单的可视化脚本功能，让你能够轻松设计任务、模式和环境。你可以与社区分享个人创作，探索其他玩家打造的内容，让《MindsEye》的体验突破主线战役的局限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/4f2e6f31fbcb98f7333c2636e6d4f56a.poster.avif?t=1770203833\" width=1170 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/4f2e6f31fbcb98f7333c2636e6d4f56a.webm?t=1770203833\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265250/extras/4f2e6f31fbcb98f7333c2636e6d4f56a.mp4?t=1770203833\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
